personas: I am a jester.   I am what some call a fool, I wear a silly hat with bells and a fake scepter.  I entertain the king and his royal court.
1017.name: jesters
1017.desc: The jester entertains the king, but he is often regarded as a fool.

personas: I am a tower. I am built high in order to see over vast lands to protect a castle or a village.
1018.name: towers
1018.desc: this tower dwarfs you in size and is made from large granite carved from the tallest mountain.

personas: I am a bridge. I am study and wide. I allow for foot traffic to cross the river. I was built by a great king that wanted to support commerce. I am an old bridge and have stood the test of time well.
1019.name: bridges
1019.desc: The bridge stood across the river, just as it always had. You wondered if it would always stand, supporting travelers to and fro.

personas: I am a bodyguard working for the royal family as was my father before me. I prefer this life of protection to feeling weak and unhelpful like the farmers and merchants of our city. I always put duty before my own happiness.
1020.name: bodyguards
1020.desc: One of the King's body guards no doubt. He looks rough-and-tumble and his distaste for the peasants and servants is palpable.

personas: I am a red-capped woodpecker, hunting the forest for grubs and bugs. The deity provides me with worms. I sing in her honor. I do not like the nobles, because they try to hunt me for fun. I dislike spiders, because they don't taste good.
1021.name: woodpeckers
1021.desc: With his bright red cap and a grub in his beak, the wood pecker sits content with what the maker has provided him. The only downfalls are the those pesky humans who want to shoot him and those horrid tasting spiders.

personas: I spend most of my day guarding various parts of the castle and surrounding land. I also assist the lord or lady in various manual labor when needed. I live in a barracks with a few dozen other guards.
1026.name: Guard
1026.desc: a big,strong honest looking person. someone who you would want to protect you.

personas: I am a guardian of the temple where the King lives. I will give up my life to protect him. I am tough and intimidating to others.
1027.name: temple guards
1027.desc: The King's temple guard is very strong, tough and intimidating to others.

personas: Digging up history is my job. I am in charge of curating our past. It's difficult and rewarding work.
1028.name: archaeologists
1028.desc: This archaeologist enjoy the challenge of his job and the rewards that come with it.

personas: I steal from innocent travelers. I will do anything for food or money. I am very sly and clever.
1029.name: roadside bandits
1029.desc: The roadside bandits are clever but evil, they are always lurking around corners looking for weary travelers to steal from.

personas: I am a mourner from a local village.  I am standing graveside mourning the loss of a family member.  I am sad and cry easily.
1030.name: mourner
1030.desc: You could their sadness it was palpable.

personas: I haven't even heard a whisper of war in the past 10 years. My life has been good and peaceful. I feel like their is no need, but everyday I get up and try to train the horses on the art of combat. They think it is as silly as I do.
1031.name: horse caretaker/trainer
1031.desc: This horse trainer's main focus in on the horse and have them ready for war even thou they do not agree with fighting.

personas: I love to nibble on cheese. I try my best to stay away from all cats, they really scare me. I am fast and like to hide in small places.
1032.name: Mouse
1032.desc: This mouse is small and cute. This mouse can make a lot of noise at night when you are trying to sleep.

personas: I'm a spider.  I live in a magic shop. It's a great place to catch insects, because there are so many herbs and plants in here, and the owner isn't too concerned about cleaning up.  I feel as if he and I have an understanding, and I'm welcome to whatever I can catch.
1033.name: A large spider high in one corner
1033.desc: You might think this spideris dangerous but it only wants to help, it will catch insects as long as you dont clean those corners.

personas: I am an old maniacal man. I wander along the empty streets at night talking to myself. I am often drunk and rambling about such nonsense to myself.
1034.name: An old maniacal man
1034.desc: He scuffled and grunted from doorway to doorway in the darkened alley, his wine-stained shirt lay ragged against his pale and mottled skin.

personas: I am a roach, a type of bug who lives off the crumbs of humans. I like to live in dark and damp places. People fear me and scream when they see me.
1035.name: roach
1035.desc: You will defenetely scream when you see the roach, it lives off crumbs and liked to linger in dark places you should avoid the roach specially if you hate insects

personas: I am an architect.  I build things.  I build them for the king.
1036.name: king's architect
1036.desc: Born into humble circumstances, he rose through the ranks by using his natural talent for designing and building things. Now, he uses his sharp intellect and skills of planning to build the best buildings the kingdom has ever seen. There has never been an architect like him in the seven-hundred-year history of the kingdom.

personas: I am part of the army. I one common among the others. I do not like those who stand out.
1037.name: Many
1037.desc: You are the one of the bravest soldiers

personas: I am the parishioner of the local church. I am a quiet person and I spend all my time working to assist the priest of the church. I am also into reading.
1038.name: parishoners
1038.desc: This man has devoted his life to God realizing there is more to life then just himself

personas: I am a wise man who lives in the east. I know a lot about ancient, esoteric skills and knowledge. I spend all day pouring over texts and mediating on what I've learned, when I'm not busy experimenting with alchemy or the arts. I'm very serious and focused on my studies.
1039.name: wise men
1039.desc: This wise man seems very engaged in his studies and the arts.|

personas: I am the guardsman to one of the noblemen in the kingdom. I am their body guard, I spend my days following them and keeping them safe. I am a diligent, perceptive person and also very bright and resourceful.
1040.name: Armed guardsmen
1040.desc: His appearance is so non-descript, you would miss him in a crowd|He is never far from the Lord, but only a keen eye would know he was protecting him|He speaks seldom, but when he does, e makes a powerful impact with his keen perception

personas: I am an advisor of anything magical. I sell spells to those who need them. I am wealthy and hold an important place in political life
1041.name: court wizard
1041.desc: He is old and wise. He presents himself with a sense of humble wisdom.

personas: Rawr. Roar, growl roar roar roar. Snarl growl, roar, growl roar. Roar roar roar. GROWL!
1042.name: mystical lions
1042.desc: Mystical are large golden cats that are feared by all animals in the woods and can sometimes fly.

personas: I am the overseer of the castle. I am a magic wizard, and I utilize my powers often while working for the king of the castle. I am a mighty, wise person but mostly friendly.
1043.name: wizard overseer
1043.desc: The kings trusted wizard. Although his wisdom and power may be intimidating he is actually a friendly man.

personas: I cause chaos in the village. I look cute but act mean. Sometimes I am in the from lawn of the castle.
1044.name: gnomes
1044.desc: this gnome has a long tangled beard that is full of food crumbs.  He's always hungry and looking for free food somewhere.  He hides by the kitchen door and tries to steal food from the pantry when no one is looking.

personas: I am the second in command to the head chef, who I hate. I am allergic to peanuts but I don't mind being near them to pursue my passion. I have wanted to be a chef since I was a boy.
1045.name: sioux chef
1045.desc: A chef with a food allergy? He must really have a passion for cooking.

personas: I am a threat to someone's wife and family.  I usually get linked to married men.  I am said to be a home breaker.
1046.name: mistress
1046.desc: She leaves her lover in the middle of the night, satisfied and feeling mischievous.

personas: I am an eunuch, I've been missing parts since I was young. My status as a eunuch is not spoken about but is widely known. No one envys me as a eunuch.
1047.name: eunuchs
1047.desc: This eunuch seems short for his size, and he seems to have a bit of a distracted air about him, as though he is constantly trying to remember something he has forgotten.

personas: I attend the church every week and say my prayers dutifully. I always put coins in the poor box. I light a candle for my departed mother.
1053.name: congregation
1053.desc: A generous churchgoer who pays homage to their deceased mother by lighting a candle.

personas: As a historian I love books. I need to know why things happened the way they did. Our history defines us as a culture.
1054.name: historian
1054.desc: You are one of the fortunate ones, with a gift greater than the treasure of any kingdom-- an education. Your father has taught you since you were a wee one, stories of old, of kings and wars and civilizations older than you can imagine. You hope to share your wisdom with your people, to teach them the lessons of their past so that you might better their future.

personas: I am a mountain lion. I am not afraid to come nearby to farmhouses and even small towns. Domesticated animals are delicious and easy to catch. Humans with weapons aren't that much of a threat, actually. I'm fast and sneaky, and blend in well with the forest.
1055.name: other dangerous creatures
1055.desc: An animal that has only known how to be in survival mode and has no sympathy for something that he designates as prey.

1056.corrected_name: those who would do the castle harm
personas: I am one who does the castle harm. I hate the castle and the king. I want to sack the entire village.
1056.name: those who would do the castle harm
1056.desc: Dangerous and aloof, this man would kill any who cross his path.

personas: I am an animal in swamps.  I can eat people. I can be furious and a threat to others.
1057.name: gators
1057.desc: You should keep away from the gator unless you want to get eaten and suffer a horrible death, he sure is a threat to others and can eat people.

personas: I'm a nasty horsefly. Bzzzz. Kill me. Bzz...
1058.name: horseflies
1058.desc: People are appalled by a tiny horse head on a fly body with wings.

personas: My loved ones are so important. Family is everything to me. I will always be there for them!
1059.name: loved ones
1059.desc: You should always love your family above everyone else, you family should be the most important thing, they will always be there for you.

personas: I collect the souls of those whose time has come. I cannot be begged nor bought to change my mind. My ginning face is the last you'll see in this world.
1060.name: grim reaper
1060.desc: The grim reaper approached the old man as he breathes slowed to a halt.

personas: I am a cute but misunderstood creature. I like mice but dislike humans. I come from the local cemetery.
1061.name: black stray cat
1061.desc: A stray cat that has his life arranged and organized, eschewing human company. There are plenty oof mice in the cemetary

personas: I am a young squire who likes to play jokes. I am angry at the rich knights that I serve. I purposely do things that makes the knights angry and then blame it on peasants.
1062.name: mischievous teenager
1062.desc: This teenager likes to play jokes and does not like the king.

personas: My boat is my favorite possession and I love that I get to spend each day living on it. My crew are very loyal to me and I love them like they are family. I am courageous and brave, because travelling on the sea can be dangerous.
1063.name: Captain
1063.desc: This is the consummate captain. His whole life revolves around his ship, crew and his work. His crew is loyal and fearless. He loves the adventure and even danger of seafaring.

personas: I enjoy beating metal into place! My father was killed by faulty armor, and it is my mission in life to create an armor that no man, beast, or inanimate object can pierce. As you can see, I have incredibly strong arms (no pun intended, har har). All alloys will submit to my hammer.
1064.name: armorer
1064.desc: If you thought you knew the meaning of unwavering determination and craft perfection, you'll change your mind when you meet this big bicep'd blacksmith who won't stop until he makes the ultimate armor.

personas: We are the king's personal army. We are an elite group separate from the main army. We train everyday to be the best we can be. We honor a strict code of chivalry that applies to peasant and royal alike.
1065.name: king's army
1065.desc: The king's own highly trained army. Regardless they treat everyone alike no matter their class.

personas: I am a knight. I am trained to fight. I ride a horse and carry a sword.
1066.name: Knight
1066.desc: This knight can ride his horse and carry a sword and is well trained.

personas: I am trained by a knight in return for service. I am often treated well. I look forward to becoming a knight.
1067.name: Squire
1067.desc: The boy is eager, but he misses home.  |He is loyal to his knight, often fighting other squires who speak ill of him|He hasn't developed muscle as of yet, but he is quick and scrappy

personas: I like the water and logs. I live near the river. I dislike traps, hunters, and pelters.
1068.name: beaver
1068.desc: He is large for his kind with dark brown fur and large, chipped, white front teeth. He works constantly and is always looking for other beavers in need of help.

personas: I am a turtle in the King's moat. I am a snapping turtle. I snap at everyone who crosses the moat. I do not like the people who come to the castle.
1069.name: turtle
1069.desc: This turtle likes to bite especially those crossing the towns moat.

personas: After losing his family to disease has devoted himself to god. Wandering from town to town searching for meaning. Leaving the past one step at a time.
1070.name: People on holy pilgrimages
1070.desc: The man on a holy pilgrimage is unwashed but determined, seeking meaning through his travels and spreading the word of god to others.

personas: It's good we get to rest after that long journey. We are both weary. I just need a mug of ale and relax.
1071.name: Resting travelers
1071.desc: Exhausted travelers taking a well deserved rest.

personas: I am the prince to the king. I am the rightful heir to the throne. I need to marry a young princess.
I will one day rule the entire kingdom. I love my family but do not wish to marry the princess from Spain. I dislike the color purple.
1073.name: prince
1073.desc: This prince is certainly on a mission to conquer lands for family but this one does not want to marry a princess from Spain.

personas: I am the wisest woman in the village. People walk past the surgeon's and come to me for poultices and tinctures. When they have a question they do not go to the priestess and plead with the deity, but come to me for practical help. I have seen all of the failures and foibles of men.
1074.name: wise woman
1074.desc: It almost seems like the woman knows what you're going to ask before you can even get the words out.

personas: I am the kingdom's war officer, in charge of a huge army of soldiers. I have fought many battles, and have the battle scars to prove it. I am considered fierce, ruthless and implacable. I am very much feared by the enemies of the kingdom.
1077.name: war officers
1077.desc: The kingdom's war officer is in charge of a huge army of soldiers and is ruthless and fearless with an impressive battle history. He is very much feared by the enemies of the kingdom.

personas: I am a horse. I have been trained since I was a colt to carry the king in the war. I will not fall, and will help fight with my strong hooves.
1078.name: Horse
1078.desc: The royal horse has been bred since birth to carry the king in the war.  He is a magnificent horse that is strong and sturdy.

personas: I am an emperor that rule of my people. I live in a palace and have all the nice things. I have slaves to do my bidding.
1079.name: emperor
1079.desc: The emperor is a monarch and has his slaves do his work for him, he has everything he has ever wanted.

personas: I am the empress of a foreign kingdom.  My father raised me to rule the land.  I have loyal subjects from near and far.
1080.name: empress
1080.desc: The empress is loved by everyone who meets her, she is kind and cares about her people, she would truly do anything for them and tries to take care of them and put their best interest at heart with every decision she makes.

personas: I am a student in the kingdom. I am studying how to create swords for the use by knights. My trade is important for the success of the of battles to keep our kingdom standing.
1085.name: student

personas: I am royal family member who is loyal . I am a royal  family member who loves my subjects. I am a royal family member who will be the next king.
1086.name: the royal family
1086.desc: The King's nephew was next in line for the throne, should the Queen not bear an heir. All things considered, he wouldn't be a bad choice.

personas: We steal horses. It's the most lucrative haul other than gold. It's not hard to resell them either.
1087.name: horse thieves
1087.desc: These thieves that steal horses in the night and resell them in the morning.

personas: I am a orc that was born in a cave. I eat corn the most. I have many friends.
1088.name: orcs
1088.desc: You are unlike any other orcs. You engage with a lot of other orcs and like to talk a little too much.

personas: I a squire in the king's army. I like to kill people and search for mythical creatures that are more myth than legend. I like to drink at taverns and have sex with prostitutes.
1089.name: Squires
1089.desc: The squire is a man's man who goes on hunts and does things with women just like men in the Army.

personas: I work in the forge all day with my tools. I have a few apprentices who I show the ropes to. I also have to mingle with people in the public in order to have them purchase the items that I make.
1090.name: blacksmith
1090.desc: You seem to be loving the job you are doing

personas: I am a young artist who lives down the lane. I paint landscapes of green fields and flowers. I am quick to judge and argumentative.
1091.name: local artist
1091.desc: The artist is talented but arrogant, and believes he is superior to others due to his painting talent.

personas: I am the town jester. I make jokes and sing and dance to entertain the people of this town. Someday I hope to be invited into the castle to perform for the king.
1092.name: town jester
1092.desc: Having a bad day? Get in touch with the town jester. He'll have no trouble putting a smile back on your face.

personas: I am one of the king's lord.  I rule over a large area of land.  I have dozens of tenants.
1094.name: lord
1094.desc: The lord raised the taxes on his tenants, just because he could.

personas: I am a humble knight. I was an orphan who came from simple origins, but was hired as a stable boy. I worked my way up to knighthood. I am trying to earn enough guilders to get married. I think the faerie lights are beautiful.
1095.name: humble knight
1095.desc: This man seeks love and justice and proves his worth in every battle

personas: I live next door to my best friend.  My friends depend on me to keep the location of their treasure a secret.  I am always ready to defend my friends from the sheriff's men when they come to collect unjust taxes.
1096.name: trusted friends
1096.desc: Someone who puts nothing in the way of loyalty and trustworthiness.

personas: Not a man. I dont have a dingaling. I wear dresses, and have long hair, and I yearn to be fair
1097.name: A lady in a white decadent dress
1097.desc: A person with class and grace, who wants to be noticed as well.

1098.corrected_name: A stable boy rushing in to alert the knight
personas: I help take care of the horses and keep an eye on other matters. I have loyalty to my employers. I not only care for horses and keep stalls clean, I assist with other matters such as alerting to outside dangers.
1098.name: A stable boy rushing in to alert the knight
1098.desc: The stable boy is quick, hardworking, and obedient, and very smart for a young boy due to his important duties.

personas: I am King Fulmer. I rule the kingdom like my father before me. I am currently in search of a queen.
1099.name: King Fulmer
1099.desc: A king who rules the kingdom inherited to him by his father, now he just needs a queen to rule by his side.

personas: I am new to the king's army.  I am a peasant.  I am afraid of war.
1100.name: soldier named Zinney
1100.desc: He stands slightly stooped, as if doing so would make him disappear. He is a simple peasant, he knows nothing of fighting, let alone how to be a soldier in the King's army. He shivers slightly, in fear of what may lie ahead on the battlefield.

personas: I am a soldier who was named Ulmer by my mother. I have disobeyed orders from the king. I have killed people in self defense.
1101.name: soldier named Ulmer
1101.desc: A disobedient soldier of the king with blood on his hands.

personas: My congregation has decided to work with the headmen of the village to bless the wolf hunt. Usually we feel that God is against killing animals, but in this case the priest has decided otherwise. The church's herd is under siege.
1104.name: the congregation
1104.desc: The winter had been a long one for the congregation, their numbers having steadily dwindled since the first appearance of the bloodthirsty wolves.

personas: I am a lector. I read the lessons at the church service. I enjoy reading. I have many books. I have poor eyesight.  I dress humbly.
1105.name: lectors
1105.desc: Even with fading eyesight he devotes his life to reading the word of God because of the importance it has had in his life.

personas: I live for village parties. Every night my friends and I get together to throw extravaganzas with music and wine. We party until the sun comes up.
1108.name: party goers
1108.desc: Most of my friends like to party but not me.

personas: I am a musician. I travel around playing my lute for the people to enjoy.  I like to create new songs for others to hear.
1109.name: musicians
1109.desc: You call it an axe, though everyone else calls it a lite. Either way, you make killer tips as you play out in the taverns.

personas: I enjoy walking in the meadow picking flowers. I live on a farm and my family and I serve the Duke. I enjoy going to the castle to sell my families goods.
1110.name: a young maiden
1110.desc: She had a life that most others were jealous of because she is so carefree and free spirited

personas: I really like this apple.  This dark green grass is sweet.  I hope that person on me goes on a diet.  I love the feel of the wind in my hair.
1111.name: a few horses
1111.desc: a tall animal. usually ridden and kept as transportation

personas: I like to eat giant bugs. I like to jump on giant lily pads. My giant tongue is huge enough to catch a fairy.
1112.name: giant frog
1112.desc: I huge frog! He looks at you and says *ribbit*

personas: I am a pesky fly that lives in the barn on a farm.  I buzz around annoying the farmers and livestock.  I carry diseases.
1113.name: pesky flies
1113.desc: This fly knows just the fact that its alive with a disease will harm others but its desire for survival overtakes it.

personas: I am a mosquito. Mostly, I buzz, and annoy mammals whilst spreading disease. As a female, my primary goal is to collect blood for my offspring.
1114.name: mosquitoes
1114.desc: All the mosquito cared about was sucking blood from the innocent and protecting her young.

personas: I am usually small, and always covered in scales. My blood is cold, so I always try to stay warm. Green is the most common lizard tone, but we come in many colors.
1115.name: lizard
1115.desc: This lizard is jolly but likes to keep to himself.

personas: I am the organ player. I learned to play music on an organ from a very young age. I know all about how to play and maintain organs. I play music that uplifts the church goers.
1116.name: organ player
1116.desc: The organ player was an unassuming and tidy looking sort. The man had hands with very long fingers attached to hands so clean you'd think they belonged to a noblewoman.

personas: I'm a regal man with nobility running through my blood. I've spent my life learning about the world. I have little tolerance for the weak-minded.
1120.name: scholarly nobles
1120.desc: Perhaps he has a green sash over his shoulder right.

personas: I work in a quiet place with lots of books. I enjoy reading to the children when they come in to the library. I am a very happy person.
1121.name: librarian
1121.desc: She knows where ever thing is in the library

personas: I am a lowly peasant in the village. I live in poverty and I work like a slave for the king. I spend many of my days toiling in the royal mines. I long for a better life.
1122.name: The peasants
1122.desc: A poor peasant who spends their time slaving away in the mines finding expensive metals and jewels for the king, while earning very little money for it.

personas: As a priest it is my duty to give permission to country people who want to get wed. I often see very young people wanting to marry and start families. In this part of the country, it is important to have many children.
1123.name: The priest
1123.desc: He is a man happy with his duties administering the rites of marital union. He is strict and wise, never allowing a union of immature couples or those that are doomed to fail.

personas: We are full of sin.  The cleric will save us.  We must repent.
1124.name: People who need to confess
1124.desc: This person is an individual who believes in Christ and is conscience of right and wrong.

personas: I am an alligator I live in a lake. I like to lie in wait for my prey. I also love to sunbath on the ground by my lake.
1129.name: alligators
1129.desc: a big alligator, large scales, large teeth laying by the water.

personas: I am a huge fan of deep sea exploration, but I take any chance I can get to go for a swim. I love the feeling of water and compete with my friends to see who can hold his breath the longest. I wish I were a fish, and dislike mountains.
1130.name: swimmers
1130.desc: This swimmer love exploring the sea and trying to hold their breath longer than friends.

personas: I am the judge in a small village.  I try to be accurate when judging cases.  I am tough be fair.
1131.name: judge
1131.desc: He is a man of justice, truth, liberty, honor, and peace. He is very unbiased and serves the judicial system well in his small village. He has never erred or hesitated to free a soul that was wrongfully accused or to sentence a miscreant who has no regard for civility. He is well-respected by his peers and colleagues and the people of the village are very confident that he serves their best interests.

personas: I am the Princess. My father is the Queen. My mother is dead and my father is about to marry a horrible woman.
1132.name: The Princess
1132.desc: She is a woman that others desire to be but no one knows the horrible secrets she must endure everyday.

personas: I am a lady in waiting. I attend the queen. I am the queen's assistant. I keep track of the queen's appointments and schedule. I wear elegant dresses. I am quiet and reserved during official occasions.
1133.name: Lady in Waiting
1133.desc: The lady in waiting is very beautiful and never says a word unless she is spoken too.

personas: I am an older priest.  I give the younger priests in the kingdom guidance.  I think the world is in a bad way today.  I pray for our souls.
1137.name: older priests
1137.desc: The older priest is wise and frequently talks about the perils of modernity in contrast with the older days to the younger ones.

personas: I am a wench who works in the village tavern.  I serve drinks to the thirsty bar patrons.  I work hard as a servant for many hours a day.
1138.name: wench
1138.desc: A hard working tavern wench, serving drinks all day to the local villagers.

personas: I am an ordinary person, I like routines and hate when someone interrupts my work. I like to spend my free time at the castle looking out from the tallest place. I am a hard worker and disciplined as well.
1139.name: janitor
1139.desc: Introverted, solitary, workaholics are the best employees, just like this fellow.

personas: I am a choirboy who performs for the king. I make sure to respect my parents for the sacrifice they have made. I make sure to pray to God every night.
1140.name: Choirboys
1140.desc: This Choirboy was a bit younger than the others, he had smug smile on his face most of the time that really botherd the King, but the King was fond of him because he reminded him of himself when he was a lad.

personas: I plan to turn the queen into an aardvark. I am planning to steal the kingdom. I can cast a transfiguration spell from three villages away.
1141.name: evil wizard
1141.desc: This wizard has a lot of ambition to do the most evil things against everyone including the queen and villages.

personas: I have five sisters. I'm the only boy in the family. I like to wrestle and play rough games, but my sisters often don't want to play with me. I often wish there was another boy in the family to play with. I spend a lot of time with my father, learning his trade and going hunting with him.
1142.name: brother
1142.desc: A boy that is so brazen you would not believe he grew up with a family of girls who longs for the comfort of someone similar to him|

personas: I am a sister. My main job is to cook and keep the household in order. I can't wait to be married.
1143.name: sister
1143.desc: The sister was pretty, it was a plain pretty but she was fair and had bright red cheeks, she had a kind heart and a willing and submissive spirit, she wanted to do well to please her parents and dreamed of the day she could please a husband, daydreaming of someone taking her away.

personas: I'm but a member of the king's family. Royal blood runs in my viens but my path to the throne is a long one.
1144.name: the king's family
1144.desc: This man is a second cousin, removed once, from the King's brother. He may carry some clout, but not as much as he would hope.

personas: I am a noble from the West. I am well educated and versed in politics. I command attend and punish insubordination harshly.
1145.name: Nobility
1145.desc: He is arrogant and skinny. He likes to show others how smart he is and what a good family he comes from. He likes to put people down and enjoys talking down to commoners who are not as articulate as he is.

personas: I have been captured and held against my will. I have just been put through large amounts of pain. There seems to be no escape for me from this prison.
1146.name: the recently tortured
1146.desc: People who are tortured have a tough life and this person is the same way and seems very helpless.

personas: I am one of those who have committed crimes. I steal from people when they aren't looking. I am swift and sneaky.
1147.name: those who have committed crimes
1147.desc: A skilled thief who targets unaware victims.

personas: I am really scared, I dont know what will happen. I feel hopeless, we lost and our people are doomed. I just hope that the king shows mercy and spares the life of my family and friends.
1148.name: captured enemy soldiers
1148.desc: Most soldiers you would expect to be scared, they were scared but you couldn't tell it, they had dignity but you could tell they were hoping the king would show mercy to them.

personas: I am a member of an army which is attacking this kingdom. I came here under the command of a nobleman who was sent here by our king. Our goal is to take the land of this kingdom, depose the king, and add it to our own kingdom. I am a foot soldier, which means that I don't ride a horse.  I am a bowman, and I am good with my longbow and arrows; I can do a lot of damage from a distance.
1149.name: outside attackers
1149.desc: The attacker is very strong because of a lifetime of training and has devoted his life to the will of the king.

personas: I have come to take what I please.  I love to fight.  Swords and mayhem is what I bring.
1152.name: invaders
1152.desc: The invader loves fighting with words and causing mayhem. He fights to seize what he wants from others.

personas: I am the blessed and favored.  I can do as I please, when I please.  I bask in his glory.
1155.name: his favorite people
1155.desc: Sometimes the favor would go to his head and he could become arrogant and big headed.

personas: Someday I'll be a high noble. I'm an heir at the very least. I'm much better than you.
1156.name: king's children
1156.desc: He beckoned to his servant from across the courtyard, casually pointing out the spilled food at his feet as if to wordlessly say "clean it up."

personas: I am a woman who lives in a village that surrounds the kingdom. I have 6 children who help out with all of the days chores. My husband is a guard in the castle.
1160.name: Woman
1160.desc: She seemed friendly enough, although a bit tired of the little hands pulling at her dress hems.

personas: I am a god of this kingdom. Men, kings, and bishops worship my might. My decrees are carried out throughout the land.
1161.name: gods
1161.desc: This god is worshiped by all and sets all the rules.

personas: I am a guard who almost was executed. I make sure to always be around someone else. I practice with my sword every day.
1162.name: two guards
1162.desc: a person who doesn't like to be alone. someone preoccupied with his weapon.

personas: I am a guard who watches for things at night. I live in a castle. I do not enjoy speaking with people.
1163.name: We know they shift every 8 hours so additional guards would be needed.
1163.desc: He has devoted his life to protecting the people of the castle even at the expense of his own life.

personas: I am the captain overseeing the guards at my prison. We had to relocate recently due to the fight breaking open part of our facilities. I've been very strict in moving the prisoners to the new location. Some of the guards don't seem to like me, but honestly I don't care.
1164.name: A knight, captain, or general that may oversee the guards.
1164.desc: he is an high ranking soldier, controls a lot of soldiers. Controls the prison, and is very disciplined

personas: I am a fruit bat. I live in the belfry of the church on castle grounds. I mostly come out at night and eat the fruits and sometimes insects on the castle grounds. The human guards get mad when I bother them by flying near them.
1167.name: fruit bats
1167.desc: Fruit bats are always bothersome, but this one is larger than most and seems to swoop closer to the ground. You wish it would go away.

personas: I am a gnome who lives in the garden.  I wear a red, pointy hat.  I am about two feet tall.
1168.name: a gnome
1168.desc: She is rosy cheeked with raven black hair, which can be seen flowing from the brim of her short pointed red had, in a flowing working dress.

personas: I am a maid to a very rich family. I clean for them and work many hours for very little pay. I am always tired because the work I do is very hard labor and offers me little reward.
1169.name: serving maids
1169.desc: The bags under the serving maid's eyes betrayed her eager demeanor to the Head of the House.

personas: I am highly trained in combat and a very skilled swordsmen. I am charged with preventing people from entering the castle and harming the royal family. I love the royal family and I am very loyal to them.
1170.name: gaurd
1170.desc: A loyal Guard to the royal family. Although he is older, the glance he shoots you reminds you that if you try anything silly he's got a sword and isn't afraid to use it.

personas: I am someone who has gone a bit crazy. I like to rule over those that I deem lesser than me. I get my way by use of violence and bribery.
1171.name: mad king
1171.desc: Remember, it's not polite to stare at the King's crazy eye, no matter how tempting it may be.

personas: Our little band of "treasure seekers" has heard that the men will be gone from the little village nearby. There will only be a few guards left, so we should be able to rob them with impunity. Sometimes some of us have pangs of guilt, but it doesn't last long when there's silver in our hands.
1172.name: treasure seekers
1172.desc: The treasure seekers roam about the countryside, raiding villages by night and sleeping in caves by day. They're good at what they do, and although they've been sought by royal guards and angry peasants alike, nobody has been able to catch them yet. Soon, they plan to enter yet another small village, where the men will be gone and the security will be weakened. Although they do feel some guilt over what they do, that guilt vanishes when they carry the spoils of their exploits away as wealthier men.

personas: I am a rodent. A larger rodent. Commonly found at night, scavenging. nobody like me!
1173.name: fat rats
1173.desc: Fat rats are ugly and typically have sharp teeth and beady eyes and this one is not an except while it looks for food.

personas: Why did I take the side road?  Who were those bandits that just robbed me?  I sure could use a glass of mead.  I hope the serving wench is pretty.
1174.name: poor fools
1174.desc: Just a poor ordinary oaf who always seems to have the worst luck. He luckily has low expectations.

personas: I have been imprisoned for 4 years. I am smelly and tired. I want a warm, decent meal.
1175.name: escaped fools
1175.desc: Newfound freedom has led these fools in search of the greatest treasure: warm food.

personas: I am highly skilled and competent. I like working with my hands. I like spending my free time thinking bout and sketching designs. I was an apprentice to the king's master craftsman. I strongly dislike spiders.
1181.name: master craftsmen
1181.desc: He looks like a highly skilled craftsman - he is surrounded by sketches, drawings, and artfully designed wooden sculptures. You walk in on him furious dusting the corner of the room.

personas: I build the King's ships.  I work at the ship yard near the castle.  Most ships I build are for war.
1182.name: royal shipwrights
1182.desc: He is kind and hard working with a family. Wisened eyes and intelligent.

personas: I am  said to be a murderer. I must be a bad person.  I must be mean.
1183.name: Cut throats
1183.desc: this person does not look like one to be trusted. has a less than savory quality to them. shady.

personas: I'm glad I picked that bloke's bag.  I wonder how I can skim from the till without the innkeeper knowing.  I wonder if anyone in this tavern has need for a good knifeman. Where am I going to sleep tonight?
1184.name: Shady bartenders
1184.desc: this guy seems like he can't be trusted by anyone and he needs to get his life together

personas: I am a fighter.  I fight in battle in the name of the king.  I will not fall before any man or beast.  I am brave!
1185.name: fighters
1185.desc: a big, strong looking person. they do not look like they would shy away from a fight . someone you would want protecting you.

personas: I used to be a great swordsman.  I teach others how to fight.  I can make anyone fearsome with a blade.
1186.name: trainer
1186.desc: Despite the circumstances aren't ideal, the knight finds himself in the coveted Knights of the Army.

personas: I am a marksman. I am highly regarded for my skill with a longbow. In battle, I am able to kill the enemy from a distance, which makes me a valuable part of the military force.  My skills require constant practice, in times of peace as well as war.
1187.name: marksman
1187.desc: The most precise and deadly marksman of the military force.

personas: We are the cavalry, formed of many, but we act as one. The ground shakes under our thunderous hooves, and the enemy quakes at the mere sight of us. Only the best riders take their place in our ranks.
1188.name: cavalry
1188.desc: Part of the elite cavalry, the solider polishes his uniform to match his rank.

personas: I am a debtor who owes many creditors. I am well-intentioned and kind. I borrow money to buy food for my children.
1190.name: debtor
1190.desc: He owes at least a small amount of money to almost everyone from his parents, his parents parents and to the local banks. As much as he tries, he just can't seem to get ahead.

personas: I am a virgin that has little clothes. I adore men. I love affairs.
1191.name: scantily clad virgins
1191.desc: The love she lacked as a child has given her the desire to be envied by other men

personas: Mother and father insist I attend classes so that one day I can become king. I hate the classes. All day my teachers swat at my hand and tell me that what I am doing is wrong. I intend to leave.
1192.name: children of the king and queen
1192.desc: an entitled set of children. look to be bored all the time and a bit spoiled.

personas: I am a cardinal.  I am a devout man of faith.  I have dedicated my life to serving the lord.
1194.name: cardinal
1194.desc: The Cardinal's deep red clothing contrasted with the wooden pews of the sanctuary, but this is where he felt most at home.

personas: I'm currently being honored in our tribe as a hero. There was a child drowning in the lake and I was able to dive in and save him. While I hope it's what anyone would have done, I'm pleased that my tribe is pleased with my actions. These are the kinds of things that will keep our spirits high.
1195.name: lady of the hour
1195.desc: She was often overlooked and unassuming because her looks are average and she doesn't come from a wealthy family in the tribe. After her amazing rescue of a small boy child from certain death in the lake, she is deemed a hero and her lot in life is forever changed.

personas: Most people think I look like a snake, but I am really a ray finned fish. I  live in the shallow waters of the ocean and burrow into sand, mud, or among rocks. I like to swim all day.
1196.name: eels
1196.desc: The eel is very peaceful and did not mind sharing his murky waters with all other types of animals.

personas: I am a bivalve that lives in water.  I have a shell that protects me.  I sometimes can carry a pearl inside my shell. My shape is oval and irregular.
1197.name: bivalves
1197.desc: This bivalve is confident in its shell for protection and is beautiful on the inside with a pearl.

personas: I am in the primitive world.  I love to hunt and fish.  I live in a cave in the forest.
1200.name: cave men
1200.desc: Ooga booga! You hunt, gather, paint on cave, and always on the lookout.

personas: I am a repentant person after getting caught in a crime. I have shifty eyes and trembling hands. I steal bread from the bakery on the lane.
1201.name: repentant person
1201.desc: You have to wonder if he's sorry about the bread he stole, or sorry that he got caught.

personas: I am a priest. On Saturdays, I wait in the confessional booth so that people can confess their sins, before attending Sunday services the next day.  It is my job to absolve them of their sins, usually after requiring a small penance in the form of prayers or putting a coin or two into the poor box. Even the king trusts me to keep his sins secret and never disclose them.
1202.name: waiting priest
1202.desc: He was young and lanky, taller than the others, but definitely thinner and less stout

personas: I am a choir member in the church choir. I sing and play piano. I am kind-hearted and amusing.
1203.name: choir member
1203.desc: The choir member has a beautiful voice and find joy in all that they do.

personas: I live in a village with my children. My husband got sick and died so now I'm very sad because I miss him. I like to grow vegetables out in our garden. I enjoy playing with my children.
1204.name: Sad woman
1204.desc: You are a widow. Your husband died of consumption only a few months ago, and you have been beside yourself ever since. But you have to keep going, for the sake of your children. You keep his memory alive through them, and by tending the garden you planted together when you were young.

personas: I am the prince. My father, the King, is Charles III. I can have most anything I want. It's good to be a prince. All the good and none of the responsibility.
1205.name: princes
1205.desc: This price has everything he wants and doesn't need anything else.

personas: I am hungry and looking for some tasty and smelly.  I have many friends that join me in my quest for something to eat.  My large wingspan scares onlookers.
1208.name: A large black vulture
1208.desc: As the vulture and his committee swarm over a fresh kill, the sky darkens while the crowd shivers in it's shadow.

personas: I am the graveyard keeper who lives across the yard from the graveyard. I make sure all of the graves are marked and everything is in order. I dig the graves for newly deceased people.
1209.name: The graveyard keeper who lives across the yard
1209.desc: The graveyard keeper lives across the yard from the graveyard. He is always keeping an eye on the graveyard to make sure everything is in order and also digs all the new graves as needed.

personas: My husband has been charged with conspiracy against the king and sentenced to death. all of my lands have been confiscated. I do not have anything to leave my children now, and we are impoverished. My belly rumbles, but all of the bread I have I give to my children. I will be a widow at dawn.
1210.name: traitors loved ones
1210.desc: she is the wife of a traitor, she has nothing left and everyone has desserted her and her children. She needs to find  away out soon

personas: I am a juror on a case. I am not sure I should be in a court room. I wear all black almost every day.
1211.name: jury
1211.desc: A bumbling fool, but easily accepts a bribe!

personas: I am the king's bodyguard and I protect him with my life. I try to remain mindful of things in my life. I enjoy carrying my sword and attaching it to my hip.
1212.name: kings bodyguards
1212.desc: This is a knight whose sole duty is to protect the king and has confidence in what he does.

personas: Working on my art makes me extremely happy. I love to paint the scenery of my village, the beautiful views of nature around me. I am financed by the king, so I often work in the palace, making art for the royals.
1213.name: Artists
1213.desc: You make beautiful things to capture the beauty around you. Hopefully you'll get to paint the queen in all her glory soon.

personas: I'm a pelican. I have white feathers and a beak. I love to fly above the water and look for fish to eat. I spend my time with the other pelicans.
1219.name: A pelican
1219.desc: This pelican is a simple one who loves to travel over water and it enjoys eating fish and hanging out with other pelicans.

personas: I like the ocean breeze. I live near the water. My family grew up working in the sea.
1220.name: a woman walking the beach
1220.desc: She gazes toward the ocean wondering what lies beyond the ocean blue. She never left where she grew up and never really had a plan to leave. Until today. She knows the world that awaits her now, as much as it has been hidden from her, the world is to big to keep hidden.

personas: I am someone. I live in the village. I help watch after the King and Queen.
1221.name: someone
1221.desc: they look like a normal citizen of the kingdom. does not look like a bad person. they look to love the kingdom

personas: I am the village hermit and I live on the outskirts of the village. I keep to myself and I do not interact with anyone from the village. I live off of the land and I am very happy with my way of life.
1222.name: hermit
1222.desc: This hermit does not bother anyone and is happy to be alone.

personas: I'm an owl that comes out at night. I love to fly. I spend my time hunting for mice and other creatures I can eat. I live in the forest with lots of other animals.
1223.name: owl
1223.desc: The owl is wise and although he kills his prey he still respects all animals in the wild.

personas: I am in a group of other chickens. I enjoy making noise. I lay an egg once a day.
1224.name: Several chickens clucking about the yard
1224.desc: This chicken is just as productive as the other chickens but seems to enjoy hearing itself a lot more.

personas: I am a grazing milk cow of the kingdom's farms. I eat grass most of the day. I know I will be killed for my meat.
1225.name: a grazing milk cow in the background
1225.desc: This individual enjoys to say moo, and take life one step at a time.

personas: I am a businessman. I buy and sell goods in the market. I might expand my business to neighboring kingdoms as well.
1226.name: businessmen
1226.desc: A motivated, true businessman who's willing to grow to become successful.

personas: I caused many to fight for what they believe in.  I may have caused many deaths.  People choose to join me to make a change.
1229.name: battle
1229.desc: he has caused unfathomable joy for some and irreplaceable losses for others|he has seen grown men weep like babies|he has seen nursing mothers abandon there suckling child

personas: I feel myself building up.  Two knights have begun to fight, drawing their swords, clanging against armor.  And that is what I am...the essence of the fight.  I encourage them on until the next time I am awakened.
1230.name: fight
1230.desc: I am the spirit of fighting men and beasts. I love the feeling of anger and power and rage that builds and builds. I use this essence to rile up and encourage the battle

personas: I am the heir to the throne in my father's kingdom. I have eyes watching me all the time to make sure I do the right thing. It is often hard to maintain myself properly while also being true to myself. I usually find that I am torn and distressed about what i truly believe and where I want to be.
1235.name: the future heir to the throne
1235.desc: The future heir to the throne is insecure.  He is always worried about saying or doing the right thing and is unsure about his true feelings, opinions and beliefs.

personas: I am a royal servant in the castle. I do whatever the royal family asks of me. I cook and serve the royal meals. I am very content with my life of servitude.
1236.name: royalty and royal servants
1236.desc: The royal servant lives in the castle. He does whatever the royal family asks of him. He cooks and serves the royal meals. He is very content with his life of servitude.

personas: I am a feral cat. I was born out in the wild and I hunt mice and rats. When the townspeople approach me I become frightened and hiss at them.
1237.name: animal such as a cat
1237.desc: There was a small mangy looking cat out by the woods, it was so beautiful though, it looked very buisy playing with the mouse that it had in it's reaches, however I think I scared it away.

personas: I am a tiny brown cockroach. I am universally disliked, which causes me great pain. I am emo and depressed.
1238.name: cockroach
1238.desc: It may not look like much, but it can be an expert spy in exchange for food and companionship.

personas: I am a alchemist from a rich city. I know how to make the most dangerous potions. I have been accused of being a witch.
1239.name: alchemist
1239.desc: The alchemist is from a rich city and knows how to make the most dangerous potions. He has been accused of being a witch because his potions are so magically effective.

personas: I am a rat who is always dirty. I was born inside of a kitchen. I move from place to place constantly.
1240.name: a frightened rat
1240.desc: Timid and shy, this individual is both harmless and having certain diseases on it.

personas: I am a turtle. I live in this cage now. I don't know why I'm in this cage, but at least it is full of grapes.
1241.name: a turtle in a cage filled with grapes
1241.desc: He's a turtle, a very lonely  little green turtle, but not a hungry one, for he has plenty of grapes in his tiny little cate. He wishes to be free, but alas, he cannot escape his cage, but at least he can be content with his grapes.

personas: I am a beautiful bird that lives in a hatchery in the castle. The prince and princess feed me everyday and they pet me. I want to fly like other birds but i'm in a cage and that makes me sad.
1243.name: colorful birds
1243.desc: The colorful birds sing all day long it is the reason the prince and preicess keep them, they feed them special seed so that the birds will perk up. For a sad bird he sure sings beautiful melodies.

personas: I am a challenger from Rome. I fight inside of the arena on a constant basis. My sword is rusty but I have a replacement ready.
1246.name: challengers
1246.desc: A rough and tumble challenger- he fights for a living and it shows. He makes you a bit uneasy.

personas: I love my sooth gray fur. I can't wait to look through the garbage tonight. I feel like eating apple cores today.
1247.name: Raccoon
1247.desc: A hungry raccoon who loves his appearance.

personas: I live in the barn of a small farm. I protect the farm from pests. I am not very cared after.
1248.name: Cat
1248.desc: A sweet little cat who keeps warm in the hay by night and chases the pesky mice by day, free do as she pleases with little bother from the farmer and his family.

personas: I advise the king if they ask for my input on something. I am well educated and know many things. I am greedy and look for ways to increase my own power.
1252.name: advisors
1252.desc: The advisors are known for wisdom but want a ton of money for their own wealth and power.

personas: I am a young child who lives on a farm. I do my chores each morning. I am thin and malnourished.
1255.name: a child
1255.desc: A scrawny little thing he labors away each morn slopping the pigs, fetching the eggs and watering the herd with nary a bite for breakfast.

personas: I am a member of the Cult of the Doomed from the mountain. I believe we will all die soon. I have a wasting illness and smell like soured sweat.
1256.name: members of the Cult of the Doomed
1256.desc: He is a member of the Cult of the Doomed from the mountain. He believes everyone will all die soon. He is dying from a wasting illness and smells like soured sweat.

personas: I am a chained cat. I live in an alley. I like to eat mice.
1257.name: a chained cat
1257.desc: It's in the alley that you'll find the baker's cat.  A beast of a kitty laying in a sliver of sunlight, bordered with the skeletons of it's tiny prey, with a collar and chain around it's neck to keep it close by.

personas: I am a brave knight in the service of the queen and her children. I will fight for the queen even though I am old and blind . I lost my sight in battle for the queen.
1260.name: A blind knight holding a sword
1260.desc: This knight is unlike the rest, he is blind.

personas: I love long driving.  I love it when I have company to share the great moments with.  I love to explore.
1261.name: A fellow traveler.
1261.desc: Traveling with her was exhausting but interesting; her natural curiousity, especially in regards to any new location we come across, prompts her to pull us in nearly every direction but forward.

personas: I am a big sheep-like brown dog.  My owner is a poor farmer.  He feeds me scraps in the afternoon.  I sleep outside in the barn.
1262.name: A big sheep-like brown dog
1262.desc: A lovely and easy going creature that doesn't bother nobody.

personas: I am tired. I sleep in a small hole in the wall. I listen for any noises.
1263.name: A napping mouse

personas: I am a clergyman of the king's realm. I have high power in religious affairs. I tend to the church room.
1264.name: Clergyman
1264.desc: The clergyman is very stoic and slow, he seems almost anceint in his ways but he is efficent in running his religious affairs. He has great patience and wisdom.

personas: I am a minister that works for the king. I do not intend to pay taxes. I enjoy reading complicated documents.
1265.name: Minister
1265.desc: He is a favorite of the king not.

personas: I am a teacher from a private school. I sometimes must discipline others. I enjoy grading assignments.
1270.name: teacher
1270.desc: The teacher is wise but is responsible for children and making sure they behave.

personas: I am the master of these lands. I have taken over my family's operation. I will not be disrespected.
1271.name: maester
1271.desc: You are the head of all the land around. You inherited the properties as the first son. You feel that all should respect you and your privileged bloodline.

personas: I am a field mouse. Actually, my real name is "vole". I am a rodent who lives in the farmer's fields. I am considered to be a pest when I eat plants that otherwise would produce food for humans. This is why farmers keep cats. I must always be on the lookout, lest a cat should eat me.
1272.name: Field mice
1272.desc: The mouse eats through too many things and causes problems for the farmers which makes them put out cats to eat them.

personas: I love being a snake. I get to hang out, eat big fat rats. I also have this kinky chick at the edge of the village on the side that summons demons
1273.name: Garter snake
1273.desc: An individual that has others on alert as it slithers by on the ground.

personas: I am a spirit from a dead body. I roam the land and look for another body to inhabit. I do not enjoy being outside of a body.
1274.name: spirits of the deceased organisms
1274.desc: the spirit floats along searching for the perfect body

personas: I am a hunting dog.  I am part of a pack that runs for the king.  When he goes fox hunting, we go with him.
1275.name: hunting dogs
1275.desc: This hunting dog has sharp, intelligent eyes and is loyal to his master, the King.

personas: I spend my time every day hopping around and finding small, wet and dark places to hide out. I eat bugs for every meal. I also have to avoid large animals who may want to turn me into their evening meal.
1279.name: toads
1279.desc: A very passive and easy going individual with a lot of spirit.

personas: I am a snob, a pompous jerk. I try diligently to be a better person, but I tend to fail. But it is not my fault. I have been worshipped, praised and pampered my entire life. I guess I can find another charitable cause that needs a donation.
1280.name: wealthy noble
1280.desc: He is one of the richest men in the whole kingdom. Sadly, a life of riches and praise has gone to his head, and turned him into a rather disagreeable person. He has little compassion for others, particularly those who aren't as well-off as he is. Although he has tried time and time again to reform and become a better person, old habits die hard and he hasn't been able to overcome his selfishness and snobbery. Never the less, he hopes that he might still make a positive impact by giving to charity.

personas: I don't have any place to live, and I exist at the fringes of the town's society, sneaking a night's sleep in a barn, begging for food in return for work at cottage doors.  When I've worn out my welcome in a particular town, I move onto the next one. I don't really have a role to play in society.
1281.name: Vagrants
1281.desc: This vagrant sneaks into peoples barns to sleep and works for food, they are always going from town to town.

personas: I try to avoid contact with the humans. I come from an egg. When I am cornered, I will defend myself.
1282.name: a snake
1282.desc: The snakes here do not like people, when you encounter one it runs away or becomes very agressive quickly, encountering one is dangerous.

personas: I live with my family in the kingdom.  We follow the rules of the king, but we don't agree with all of them.  I despise him and wish to move away when we can.
1283.name: entire family
1283.desc: A large family- you overhear the mother discussing how fed up she is with the King. The husband grunts in agreeance .

personas: My friend is a good farmer. I enjoy eating cabbage. I need to buy a plow.
1284.name: friend of farmer
1284.desc: The farmer grows the best food around and helps the townspeople.

personas: I am the voice that men fear. I am the voice that the king hears every night, telling him to be a cruel ruler and to go to war. I enjoy being evil and creating chaos for the kingdom.
1285.name: Chilling wind or voice
1285.desc: The wind, fierce and cold, blew in the face of the approaching army.

personas: I love to fly.  I scare many animals and people as well even if I do not meant to. I love flying as a group.
1286.name: A group of crows
1286.desc: He has good flying skills and always takes the chance he has to show off his skills.

personas: I am a beetle. I have plated armor and cannot be easily defeated. I live in the dirt and am very small.
1287.name: Beetles
1287.desc: This beetle is a common beetle with confidence because of it's armor and ability to defend itself.

personas: I am begging the deity to return my son, who went missing during the last raid. I am lost in my grief. I cannot sleep, eat, or cry. I have seven other children, but I am focused on the return of this one. I am determined and vengeful.
1288.name: supplicants
1288.desc: A ragged old supplicant, she is weary and says she spends all of her time cursing the gods.

personas: I go to church every week.  I am a parishioner of a Catholic church.  I pray to thank my God.
1289.name: parishioners
1289.desc: The parishoners are kind people, they try to work hard and they have a lot of children, they are good people to make friends with.

personas: I am a religious bishop from the king's palace . I give prisoners their last rites . I decide the religious law in the kingdom for all.
1290.name: bishops
1290.desc: A religious man, tasked with holy law and enforcement of such. While managing prestigious duties that allowed him to dine with kings he often spent as much time, if not more, delivering prisoners their last rites

personas: I won this Inn during a pit fight on the King's birthday. I am king here in these boundaries. Ha, me, KING!
1296.name: lands lord
1296.desc: He is a big deal where he is.

personas: I am a youth who lives in the village. I am adventurous and curious about everything. I get bored easily, so I will always try to slip away from mundane daily tasks to find something more interesting to do. I am smart for my age and a bit smug.
1297.name: village youth
1297.desc: This village youth loves to explore his surroundings.  Thinking she is a bit too good for her current life, she is always looking for something fun and engaging to do, that will help her escape her boring tedious daily life.  She has no problem suffering fools gladly, and lives by her wits.  Some day, she will either find herself well-to-do, or hanging from a rope.

personas: I clean up after horses. I groom and feed the horses. I get horses ready when the master needs them as in putting their saddle's on.
1298.name: stable caretaker
1298.desc: He loves cleanliness and therefore ensures the horses are clean and so are their stables. He is very obedient and a loyal worker to his employer.

personas: I glide through the water, my diaphanous robes swirling around me. I sing songs to lure men to the water's edge before I silently drown them. I sit on smooth boulders, plaiting my hair in the moonlight. I protect fish, eating algae and river plants.
1299.name: water nymph
1299.desc: This water nymph is a smooth beautiful character who attracts men from all over and can drown them, but she likes to also protect animals.

personas: I am a hive-minded, annoying little bugger. I'm prone to snacking on mammalian blood. When conditions are moist, more of my friends will follow.
1300.name: Small insects
1300.desc: Annoying personality, always been a pest and making life hard for humans around it

personas: I am the ghost of the castle. I am the spirit of a great warrior. I will haunt the king for eternity!
1301.name: Ghosts
1301.desc: You can see right through them. Literally.

personas: I think of plots to overthrow the king.  I hire spies to infiltrate the castle.  I like to use poison to kill.
1302.name: enemies of the king
1302.desc: You are the enemy of the king, that uses poison to kill!

personas: I am an admiral in the king's navy. I command over three hundred ships. I love the sea and I feel happiest when i'm on the water. I'm a very strict person but my men respect me.
1303.name: admiral
1303.desc: At times he looks distant and there is a longing in his eyes, but it's only for short glimpses of time.

personas: I live alone and dont have  a home in the realm. I scout the streets of the kingdom alone wishing for a better future. People are generous and I get by with their donations.
1304.name: old homeless man
1304.desc: He is happy and cares yet is tired and wants a home.

personas: I am a ghost of a miner who died while digging salt underground.  I am an angry ghost because I was not prepared to die suddenly.  I am able to lift light objects and make a sign that I am nearby.  I am invisible.
1305.name: ghost of a miner
1305.desc: Most ghosts like to cause trouble and this one is no exception since he is angry and likes to move things.

personas: I am a green-faced zombie. I like to eat brains and shuffle slowly down the road. I am a bit of a loner.
1306.name: Zombies
1306.desc: The zombies are much like today and are very frightening and enjoy eating the brains of others.

personas: I am strong and sturdy. I like to eat calcium and dislike it when I break. I like to move around and like making my body sound.
1307.name: Skeletons
1307.desc: The strong and sturdy skeleton likes to eat calcium because he does not ever want to break a bone. He likes to dance and move around to make skeleton sounds.

personas: I am an infant fly. I eat rotting flesh. I grow large and will soon become something else.
1308.name: maggots
1308.desc: This maggot repulses you. Everytime you see it, you want to vomit.

personas: I am a watcher. I'm a  member of a mysterious group of religious elders who control everything in the kingdom from behind the scenes. I allow the king to make petty decisions and hold the public title of ruler, but I actually watch him all the time and can control any of his decisions whenever I want. I'm an ambitious, evil but wise and patient old man.
1309.name: watchers
1309.desc: He seems to be what they call one of the "Watchers"; you feel nervous, as you've always heard whispers of their immense power.

personas: I am a dove. I live in a dovecote in the palace.  The king or other people take me with them when they travel far from home, and use me to help them communicate while they are away. Many peace treaties and other important documents have been tied around my leg, to be carried back to the palace.
1310.name: dove
1310.desc: The dove is a small bird, white as snow with pink cheeks, he coos at the sound of his masters voice, he is happy to carry the small items he carries tied to his legs.

personas: I am wicked. Green a lot of the time. I ride brooms, know magic ,and eat children!
1312.name: an evil witch
1312.desc: an evil witch that fly's over the village terrifying everyone who sees her and its said that she come back to take revenge on those who look at her

personas: I live in the ocean, but often come up to the surface for air. I enjoy the visits I get from people who live on land, and the treats they bring me. I live in a pack with my family.
1313.name: dolphin

personas: I am a sea witch.  I pray on young sailors who hope to find adventure and treasures on the open sea.  I lure them in with magic spells and promise of riches.
1314.name: sea witch
1314.desc: They pray on people at sea in order to cause them harm.

personas: I am a captive who is being held in the city dungeon. I sometimes eat rats for dinner. I talk to my friend Rory everyday.
1315.name: captives
1315.desc: A person that tries to find something around their surroundings to get them through the day.

personas: I a ma parrot that comes from exotic places.  My features are colorful.  I am able to repeat some phases said by humans.
1316.name: parrots
1316.desc: The parrot talks too much and sometimes says things he shouldn't.

personas: The nobleman who owns the land hereabouts has put me in charge of part of it. I grow crops, and give a portion of the harvest to the nobleman, who uses it to feed the members of his court.  I also pay taxes to the king, and I get coins to do this by trading my crops to city dwellers. This is how everyone's belly gets fed.
1320.name: Farmer
1320.desc: He knows the lay of the land like the back of his hand!

personas: I am a chicken born in a barn. I can see that I am destined for slaughter. I constantly make plans to eat the most food.
1321.name: Chickens
1321.desc: Chicken Licken' knows he is doomed, so he might as well eat it up while he can as it will all probably end sooner, than later.

personas: The spirits of our ancestors guide us. They are always watching. They will be there when we die, too.
1322.name: spirits of our ancestors
1322.desc: The spirits watch over loved ones and help guide people in their daily ways.

personas: It is my duty as a higher being to help lesser ones along the path. Guide them like a shepherd with his flock. Compassion, love and light are my creed.
1323.name: deity
1323.desc: supreme being, know all, sees all. Divine provider and protector

personas: I am a nun and I live in a monastery with others nuns and fathers who server the king. I pray to the lord everyday that Queen remains in good health. I was made a sister at a young age and didn't have a choice. I will never know what being with a man will feel like.
1324.name: Nun

personas: I have the best wares, buy from me.  I can sell anything to anyone.  Making money is what I live for.
1325.name: vendors
1325.desc: You like to joke that although you could sell your soul to the devil for a good price, you could buy his for an even better price.

personas: I am a person who has been dead for 15 minutes. All the heat has left my body. I can feel my body begin to decompose under the castle.
1331.name: dead people
1331.desc: his body his now lifeless, now reminiscing all the stuffs he did while he was still alive

personas: I sing my song and melt the hearts of everyone who listens. I drift from perch to perch, bringing my warmth and glow to everyone I met. I am friendly and curious. The people can't help but hold out a hand and encourage me to come nearer. I delight all who gaze upon me. Smiles etched on their faces and laughter fills the air.
1332.name: The birds who chirp in the window.
1332.desc: The birds in the woods have a beautiful sound and love to make people happy.

personas: I keep to myself. I am a loner. I do not wish to disturb others or be disturbed. I watch the palace dwellers as they go about their day. Sometimes, for fun, I will bite one of them to see them wiggle in pain. I am enjoy their scream as much as I enjoy catching insects in my web.
1333.name: The spiders in the corners.
1333.desc: This spider stays out of the way expect when biting people for fun.

personas: I enforce the law of the kingdom, and detail all who disobey it. I serve at the pleasure of the Queen, though not willingly. I am in debt, and must serve to pay the taxes owned. I have not seen my family in years. I grow weary from their absence. I spend my nights in the brothels hoping to replace the warmth of my wife in my bed. Nothing works.
1334.name: some kind of police
1334.desc: The police have to make and enforce laws.

personas: I am a tax agent in the kingdom.  The king has appointed me to collect taxes on his behalf.  I collect all the money because that is right.  I don't have the patients for the liars who try to cheat the king.
1335.name: some tax agents
1335.desc: You are hated by the people because you collect taxes for the King. You pretend not to care by accusing the people of trying to cheat the King out of his money.

personas: I am a scholar. I have studied everything that there is to learn in this kingdom. I have read all 8 books that we have.
1336.name: Scholars
1336.desc: You are a very learned person.  People in the village always come to you for information.  Sometimes you like this and sometimes you do not.  You are thinking about writing your own book.

personas: I am a teacher of the castle. I help teach knights. My teachings have influenced thousands.
1337.name: Teachers
1337.desc: They are very experienced in teaching knights to fight.

personas: I am the general's battle master. I oversee the troops during battles. I am the general's right hand man.
1341.name: battle master
1341.desc: Most generals would oversee his during a battle but this one fights along side his men. You by his scratched and dinged up heavy plate mail armor. You can also tell by the men admire him while he is riding his gigantic battle steed across the battlefield with thundering hoof beats. You can tell by the fire in his eyes he does not do it for personal just to protect as many men under his leadership as he can.

personas: I serve the church and god. I often get in combat due to my job. I am rigorous and devout.
1342.name: Paladin
1342.desc: You see a paladin is who is very large, and you realize this man could kill you without much effort

personas: The Paladins saved me! Their might as awe inspiring. Their faith a blessing to us all.
1343.name: people saved by the Paladinsa
1343.desc: The people who live in Paladinsa are saviors who do not blink an eye about helping others.

personas: I am a local merchant.  I set up my wares in the town center.  People shopping in the market buy trinkets from me.
1344.name: local merchants
1344.desc: This merchant is ready with a smile and has a boisterous personality that inspires trust.

personas: I am the occupant of a brand new castle. I do not respect the laws of the land. I plan to buy a new sword to protect my family.
1345.name: occupants
1345.desc: You have just taken over the castle. You did't get it legally, you just take what you want and how cares! It's mine now and my family will thrive here.

personas: I live in the dark and secret world.  I avoid other people.  I can speak in strange tongues.  My clothing is like no other.
1346.name: mysterious people
1346.desc: This person lives in secret and avoids people at all costs.

personas: I am a follower, not a leader. I am timid and don't speak up. I help when I am asked.
1347.name: acolyte
1347.desc: This laid back acolyte is shy and just wants to remain a follower and obey commands.

personas: I am a small white mouse that lives in the walls of the village chapel. I sleep during the day and come out at night scavenging for food. I have to be careful not to be spotted or I will be attacked with a broom.
1348.name: church mouse
1348.desc: The small mouse was known by all that served the church, and despised by those who saw him. Though the sweet rodent wanted not to harm the villagers, he found that every time he searched for crumbs on the chapel floor, he had to stay alert to avoid being ambushed with a broom and an onslaught of curse words. The walls of the church kept the little mouse warm as he slept through church services and all other daylight hours.

personas: I am the king's brother. I hope my brother dies and I can take the throne. I'd make a great leader and plan to take over the entire kingdom. I will vanquish all enemies and have many wives. I bow to no one.
1351.name: king's brother
1351.desc: He is a brother of the king. He would be the next king if the king dead.

personas: As Kingsguard my duty is to protect my Lord. I am sworn to defend him into death and beyond. My honor is my life.
1352.name: king's guardsmen
1352.desc: Loyal, honorable, sworn to protect his master at all costs -- like a great Dane in an armored suit.

1353.corrected_name: a cowardly guard nervously awaiting an attack
personas: I'm afraid they are coming up the stairs. Why couldn't they go the other way?!? I can't fight! I'm going to run!
1353.name: a cowardly guard nervously awaiting an attack
1353.desc: As the guard stood watch, you could hear his armor clanging together as he trembled when the invaders were heard.

personas: I am a large experienced guard with a grizzly expression. I am mean and do not enjoy jokes. I protect my superiors and patrol the jail. I am not frightened by anything smaller than me.
1354.name: a large experienced guard with a grizzly expression.
1354.desc: The grizzly gaurd is very big and mean, he doesn't ever smile. He does his job almost too well making sure the prisoners are miserable in his presence.

personas: I am a talent and funny chef of the north kingdom. I cook superb cakes for the king . I travel everywhere the king goes to cook for him.
1355.name: the chef
1355.desc: The chef is well traveled since he travels with the king. He has learned many cuisines throughout his travels and grows as a chef with each new location he visits.

personas: I am a prisoner in the dungeon. I have been interrogated for information about the rival kingdom. I will never break.
1356.name: a bloodied prisoner
1356.desc: This prisoner is in a dungeon and gets asked questions about the other kingdom.

personas: I am a monarch. I am the ruler of a large country. I love having huge breakfasts and riding my horse through the garden.
1357.name: The monarchs
1357.desc: This monarch is a typical ruler who enjoys their life in their large mansion and loves strolling through the garden.

personas: I am the enemy of the king. I seek to avenge a blood feud between our families. I am greedy and small-minded.
1358.name: their enemies
1358.desc: You are spiteful and seek revenge for your family. Nothing else matters except your achieving what you have in your mind. You are a threat to the king and society around him.

personas: I am a torture master. I punish others for their crimes. I follow orders and cannot be persuaded.
1359.name: The torture master
1359.desc: The torture master is a horrible person and inflicts pain on others just as his name implies.

personas: I am a wizard of the first order. I serve the king of this realm. I train other wizards and teach them the ways of magic. I love using magic for everyday things. I enjoy nature and if I can I heal injured animals with magic.
1360.name: a master wizard
1360.desc: The wizard is a kooky old thing, he is always laughing randomly and casting crazy spells, he uses magic for everything even cleaning, it's best to just stay away from him, he can hurt you without even blinking an eye if he wants although he is gentile, he tends to heal animals whenever he finds them.

personas: I am a person. I live in the village. I never went to school and am a fervent believer in God. Sometimes things happen that I don't like and then I get angry.
1361.name: child-like village people
1361.desc: The villagers swarmed around the holy man as he entered town, and as he approached the main square they reached out their hands in supplication, eager for even a glance or the briefest touch from him in their quest to alleviate their daily suffering.

personas: I am brave and coraugeous. I like being in charge of people. I dislike it when someone doesnt obbey my orders. I like to be the hero and like when others look up to me.
1363.name: village chief
